443
00:27:17,685 --> 00:27:19,380
- Ya Tuhan.
- Kau baik-baik saja?

444
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:20,612
- Ya.
- Kau yakin?

445
00:27:20,755 --> 00:27:22,655
Kepalaku.

446
00:27:26,361 --> 00:27:27,919
